snippet.title: The Matrix: Resurrection 2021
snippet.description:
The Matrix: Resurrection The Matrix Resurrection is an upcoming American sci-fi action film directed by Lana Wachowski, who also co-wrote the screenplay with David Mitchell and Alexander Haemon and co-produced with Grant Hill and James McTig.

Genres: Action, Science Fiction Year established: 2021 Director: Lana Wachowski
 World premiere: December 16, 2021
  Release date in RF: December 16, 2021 
Country: USA 
Studios: Warner Bros, Village Roadshow Pictures, Silver Pictures 
Duration: 148 min
